text.enText: Takataktak  Wanna run as hard as I can

text.enText: In the grass, in the sand  Your pre-race training menu

text.jpText: Turn Up! (Turn Up!) 声出せ叫べ (Wo oh oh)
text.enText: Turn up! (Turn up!) Raise your voice, shout out loud (wo oh oh)

text.jpText: トレセーン！ ファイ！ (オー！) ファイ！ (オー！)
text.enText: Tracen! Fight! (Ooh) Fight! (Ooh!)

text.jpText: たかたった 全力上がりタイム
text.enText: Takataktak  Wanna beat my own time as hard as I can

text.jpText: ゆずれない夢の途中 (Wow Wow)
text.enText: On my way to my dream I won't yield (wow wow)

text.jpText: 始めよう ここから最高STORY (Wow Wow Wow)
text.enText: Start it right here  My own greatest story (Wow wow wow)

text.jpText: (o oh o oh…おっおっおーー！)
あこがれの地へ (勇気すこし借りて)
text.enText:
To the place that I long for 
(Borrowing my courage just a bit)

text.jpText: 語り合ったMEMORY (二度と来ない今を)
text.enText:
Talking about a memory 
(The right now we won't see back again)

text.jpText: もう ドキドキもトキメキも
text.enText: Oh  These bump-a-bumps and these thump-a-thumps

text.jpText: 抑えられない たまんない
text.enText: No I can't contain  I can't get enough

text.jpText: 熱いハラハラが止まらない
text.enText: These strong tinglings just don't wanna stop

text.jpText: キミと 走り競いゴール目指し 遥か響け届けMUSIC
text.enText:
With you I  Run to the finish line striving all the way 
In the distance I already hear the music

text.jpText: ずっとずっとずっとずっと想い 夢がきっと叶うなら
text.enText:
Forever forever forever forever in my thoughts 
If my dream will be within reach soon

text.jpText: あの日キミに感じた何かを信じて
text.enText:
I'll believe in what I felt that day 
The special thing you held in you

text.jpText: 春も夏も秋も冬も超え 願い焦がれ走れ
text.enText:
Crossing springtimes 'n summers 'n autumns 'n winters 
Darting towards the wish I call my dream

text.jpText: Ah 勝利へ
text.enText: To Victory
